      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl08_LabelName\"><sub style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary);\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\" src=\"systems/sfrpg/images/cup/gameplay/photon.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></sub><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">&nbsp;</span></span><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl08_LabelName\">Photon Revelation<br /></span><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl08_LabelName\">As a move action, you can shed light in a 30-foot radius for 1 minute. You choose dim, normal, or bright light each time you activate this revelation. As a standard action, you can create a flash of brilliant light, forcin</span><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl08_LabelName\">g one creature within 30 feet to succeed at a Reflex save or be @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.tOpF6qjnlnKc10t7]{Blinded} for 1 round. Once you&rsquo;ve targeted a creature with flare, you can&rsquo;t target it with this revelation again for 10 minutes. Blind or sightless creatures are not affected by this use of this revelation.<br /><br />When you create a flash of light as a standard action and you are attuned or fully attuned, you can instead choose to make all enemies within range @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.YjE6UGzwOTfO9p4g]{Dazzled} for 1 round (no save).</span></p>"
